rows.label: qst200915_msg003
rows.name:
Everything go wrong when Kasane
around! Nothing good ever happen!
It same before, it same now!

rows.label: qst200915_msg004
rows.name: After you left, Kupon fell from cliff!

rows.label: qst200915_msg005
rows.name:
Then Tirkin attack and steal cargo!
Kupon had it up to here!

rows.label: qst200915_msg006
rows.name:
Kupon supposed to deliver
cargo today! How Kasane
take responsibility for that?!

rows.label: qst200915_msg017
rows.name:
Your cargo... It was the ingredients for
Tilly Bakery, wasn't it?

rows.label: qst200915_msg018
rows.name:
Exactly! But Kupon not have
single thing left to deliver!

rows.label: qst200915_msg007
rows.name:
There, there. Hana recommend
taking deep breaths.

rows.label: qst200915_msg008
rows.name:
It's OK. We'll get this all straightened
out, so sit back and relax!

rows.label: qst200915_msg009
rows.name:
Besides, we're filled up with good luck
thanks to all the Lucky Dawn Bread we
ate! What could possibly go wrong?

rows.label: qst200915_msg010
rows.name:
Kupon trying to tell you, this all
happen because of you!

rows.label: qst200915_msg013
rows.name:
...Never mind. If you get back
ingredients from Tirkin, then
we just call it quits, OK?

rows.label: qst200915_msg015
rows.name: Kupon just hope he can trust you...

rows.label: qst200915_msg014
rows.name:
All right guys, back we go one more
time to Tirkin Turf. It's time to get
Kupon's stuff back!
